 
<p>
  Covid in New Zealand is increasing rapidly, as <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/world/2022/jul/05/new-zealand-faces-new-covid-wave-as-experts-say-moving-on-from-pandemic-is-wishful-thinking">people can get
  reinfected just a few months after having it</a>.  Doctors call for masks,
  self-isolation, and other measures to slow the spread of the disease.

 